=Italian Game, Two Knights Defence=
==4. O-O==

White sacrifices a pawn for a lead in development and king safety. This is not the soundest line in the Italian Game, but completely playable.

'''1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Nf6 4. O-O'''
